I find this post pathetic and someone actually said they needed proof, talking about stupid. Have you forgoten that this little shit has<br>
<br>
A) use bio chemical warfare on civilians and I am talking about in the towns, this means women, children and the elderly too.<br>
<br>
B) has invaded 2 countries, one of which he raped {the women as well as the country} pillaged and had to be removed from by a International force.<br>
<br>
C) has killed peacfull dissenters to his being in power, including members of his own family.<br>
<br>
E) has attempted to have one of our  presidents killed<br>
<br>
F) has pledged to get revenage on the Countries that attacked him when he was in Kuwait<br>
<br>
and much much more, how much fucking proof do you need.  A electric rod up your ass with a Iraqi officer turning it on and off for kicks and giggles just ot here you scream?<br>
<br>
Christ some people have it so easy here, they think just because we are Americans that we are imune to this, I got bad new for you, we are not and if September 11th does not prove that to you, I do not know what will, you are simply blind to the point of being a danger to yourselfs and others.<br>
<br>
We have every reason in the world to go in and do this, but the best one is our past success in doing this.  Right now the entire middle east hates us, not because of our support of Israel, but of course that is not helping, but because we are the easiest and soffest target in their leaders mind.  How come there is no REAL holy war against Russia? they only invaded Afghanistan, and occupied it for what 5, 10, 15 years?  One of there brother countries, why has the focus been on us and not them, even though we helped them in their time of need? Because the consider us week, a country that will not fight back and the Russians will nuke their sorry ass's and they know it. <br>
<br>
As of right now, they have no reason not to make us the evil bad guys.  In reality, this will be a win win situation for us if Bush handles it right.  As of right now they are telling their people how bad and evil we are, that we want to attack their religion and stamp it out.  We will come over there and rape their women and kill their men, elderly and children.  Just like the Japanese did during World War II.  The similarities are scary really, give the Iraqies a  legitimate fighting force to field and they could be identical.  However, right now Japan is one of our most staunches  allies, becuase after we defeated them in War, we help rebuild their country and while doing so, prooved beyond a doubt to the people of Japan that they where lied to, still are from what I can tell, but not about us at least.<br>
<br>
This is a opertunity to do tons of good, this prick has done little to nothing with the oil wealth of the country to help his people.  Did you look at the squaler they live in, I got news for you, that is not because of desert storm, that is how there are treated and have been since the dawn of time.  What do you think will happen if we go in there and take Sadam out and rebuild that country like we did Germany and Japan after WWII?  All of a sudden the masses will have REAL hospitals to go to, they will have REAL schools to got and much much more.  But most importantly they will see first hand that we are not going to try and convert them to a diffrent religion or kill them because of theirs.  We are not there to take what they have or hurt them in anyway.  On top of that, they will see us leave them afterwards leaving them take control of their on country and rule it as they see fit, as long as it is peacefully.  <br>
<br>
Knowledge is king.  Right now, they only have the knowledge that is being fed to them by a gun point.  Take that gun a way, prove to them they were lied to and get them back on their feet and we will make at least one real friend in the area and on top of that, we will have people in the middle east, that middle easterners trust, denying the lies that are being constantley spouted about us over there.  That will help the most.<br>
<br>
I like War as much as the next guy, but you can not keep hiding under your bed and expect someone like this little shit to go away.  You either come out and beat the shit out of him or sooner or later he will come in and get you, just ask the Kuwaities if you do not believe me.  Just out of curiosity, what will your reaction be if it is your kid who dies when a bomb goes off at his school?  Just a thought to end with.<br>
